reviewText: A wonderful production perfectly acted by the incomparable Richard Chamberlain. I had not seen it in 1974, and was glad to catch up with it 44 years later. Thank you for providing the opportunity to purchase; highly recommend you and your dealership to all.
Film is fine, but the print was almost unwatchable.
GOOD FILM IN EXCELLENT CONDITION ARRIVING AND TRAVELING....BRAVO  F SCOTT WOULD BE GLAD
